{"tid":1726293,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"提議一個原則以解決大學戰線入面校內學生同外來手足嘅爭執：客隨主便","createTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:38:34.000Z","uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"851fa9eec64618a486c10403f91c17eeba1f52c2","tid":1726293,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"教育部重編國語辭典修訂本<br />\n字詞  【客隨主便】<br />\n釋義  <br />\n客人完全依隨主人的方便或安排而行事。<br />\n<br />\n開戰期間：人人平等唔分校內外, 所有人都係手足<br />\n平時守城期間：外來手足喺唔了解校內情況下, 應盡量尊重對校內有更多認識既主場人士, eg學生會, 宿生, 學生, 校友 等人嘅建議, 謙虛行事<br />\n以上絕非起大台或者分等級, 而係外來手足如果唔了解校內情況就自己衝嘅話, 只會事倍功半<br />\n有意見有野想做咪隨時提出囉, 大家同路人又唔係林鄭政府實有計傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda00fe09a442f75c91112ce1077fe21fb134891","tid":1726293,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:49:43.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第五期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1726268/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n第三&amp;四期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696271/page/1</a><br />\n第二期民調結果POST <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n眾籌link:  <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=b0a300a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXqnyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=feb7d53c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"ae9d03a3cfd205263f30ed35dfb7781abbfa3c61","tid":1726293,"uid":242605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會話<br />\n例如每兩個鐘<br />\n喺某個地方開會<br />\n投票機制<br />\n咁樣會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2771c7165d1d122eefb82185fe94537069a2f2","tid":1726293,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ae9d03a3cfd205263f30ed35dfb7781abbfa3c61","tid":1726293,"uid":242605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"會唔會話<br />\n例如每兩個鐘<br />\n喺某個地方開會<br />\n投票機制<br />\n咁樣會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"幾千人好難開會<br />\n最好就跟外面既做法, 小隊制, network咁靠tg之類形式互相協調"},{"pid":"648fcfc1b74ecb9772bc98bc24e2848466f5fbea","tid":1726293,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"****眾籌****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先64%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /